@apolcyn Can you take a look of updated code? I have updated them according to your feedbacks (thanks again). 

The key updates are:
* Use dummy socket to secure unused port
* Add used mask to ensure only useful bits are included in the flag
* Add unit test for default behavior (that's a good call)
* Use thread safe Queue to handle the exceptions
